MTD	title	Mouse liver lipidomics: control vs high-fat diet
MTD	description	Untargeted lipidomics of mouse liver tissue comparing control diet and high-fat diet groups. Samples were analyzed by LC-MS/MS on a Q Exactive HF in positive ion mode ESI. Data were processed with MS-DIAL 5.0.
